           <h1 class="title" id="page-title">“Never hang your head, girl child, raise it up high like a so”: A Conversation with Mel Pennant</h1>
      
          
    
          <div class="date-display-single">September 2, 2025</div>
    
          <div class="field-name-field-author field-type-taxonomy-term-reference field-label-inline clearfix">
        <div class="field-label"><em>by</em>&nbsp;
                              <a href="/author/renee-h-shea">Renee H. Shea</a>
                                                                                              </div>
      </div>
    
    
    
