                                                                                            <p><b>Renee H. Shea</b>, formerly professor of English at Bowie State University in Maryland, frequently contributes to <i>Poets &amp; Writers</i>, most recently a profile of Kiran Desai. She is currently doing a series for the <i>American Book Review</i> on “The Laureates.” She also coauthors English language arts textbooks for Bedford, Freeman &amp; Worth.</p>

